      <title>尽管世界领导人赞扬伊朗停火，但他们仍受到特朗普的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/08/world/europe/iran-ceasefire-world-reaction.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧洲和全球范围内，战争损害了经济，扰乱了政治，并凸显出在应对总统突发奇想时缺乏选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/08/world/europe/iran-ceasefire-world-reaction.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 09:36:38 GMT</pubDate>
