    <item>
      <title>佐治亚州和威斯康星州选举显示共和党候选人的兴趣下降</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/08/us/politics/georgia-wisconsin-elections-takeaways.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党赢得了马乔里·泰勒·格林 (Marjorie Taylor Greene) 的席位，但自 2024 年总统竞选以来，民主党将该选区向左移动了 25 个百分点。保守派候选人也在威斯康星州落败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/08/us/politics/georgia-wisconsin-elections-takeaways.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 09:02:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受到选民的刺激，共和党立法者采取行动遏制公民倡议</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/08/us/politics/republicans-citizen-initiatives.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在共和党州的公民通过投票措施保护堕胎、扩大医疗补助和提高最低工资后，州议会正在采取行动，加大此类举措的难度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/08/us/politics/republicans-citizen-initiatives.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 09:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在佐治亚州第 14 区特别决选中，民主党实现了迄今为止最大的转变</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/us/elections/georgia-house-special-shifts.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肖恩·哈里斯在第 14 国会选区落后了约 12 个百分点，但他将该选区向左移动了 25 个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/us/elections/georgia-house-special-shifts.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 02:44:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布兰奇说，只有特朗普知道邦迪为何被解雇司法部长</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/us/politics/blanche-trump-bondi-attorney-general.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[托德·布兰奇在被提升为代理司法部长后的第一次新闻发布会上表示，除了特朗普总统之外，“没有人知道”导致帕姆·邦迪被解职的原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/us/politics/blanche-trump-bondi-attorney-general.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 23:53:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的伊朗威胁看起来像是对潜在战争罪的自证其罪</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/us/politics/trump-iran-war-crimes.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统发誓要系统性地摧毁民用基础设施并消灭伊朗的整个文明，这似乎是在为他的意图提供证据。]]></description>
